data.description: Great location! Easy access to downtown, 410 and I-35. Large 4 bed, 2.5 bath home. The  primary bedroom is downstairs and includes a large walk in closet and a combined shower/bath for you to enjoy. Three large bedrooms and 2nd living area are located upstairs. You will enjoy the large backyard and patio that backs up to a green belt. Seller will contribute $5,000 for a rate buy down or help in closing costs. Sellers loan is assumable with a 3% interest rate.
